      "text": [
        " : \"إِذَا قَتَلَ اَلرَّجُلُ أُمَّهُ خَطَأً وَرِثَهَا وَ إِنْ قَتَلَهَا عَمْداً لَمْ يَرِثْهَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5684 - Asim ibn Humeid narrated from Muhammad ibn Qays, from Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), who said: \"If a man kills his mother by mistake, he inherits from her. However, if he kills her intentionally, he does not inherit from her.\""
        ]
      }
